title: Whispering Words
description:
# Whispering Words

You are given a number N followed by N words, one on each line. Your task is to output these words in reverse order, all on a single line, separated by a space. Each word consists only of lowercase letters. N is between 1 and 100, inclusive. Ensure your solution reads from standard input and writes to standard output.

## Example 1

Input:

~~~txt
5
a
b
c
d
e
~~~

Output:

~~~txt
e d c b a
~~~

## Example 2

Input:

~~~txt
3
apple
banana
cherry
~~~

Output:

~~~txt
cherry banana apple
~~~
